node.text:
@jeffsekinger came back from a addiction to now owning multiple 8-figure businesses, one of them being a crypto fund with $40M AUM. You should follow if you want to learn more about credit, funding, or crypto.

Go follow @jeffsekinger 🔥

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Business Instantly on August 14, 2021. May be a Twitter screenshot of text that says 'Jeff Sekinger @jeffsekinger In 2012, was taking out loans to feed my addiction on on Silk Road. In 2021, now own a crypto fund with $40M AUM. Here's how we got to this point...'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jeff JeffS Sekinger @jeffsekinger I'll keep this short short and sweet. When was in college, had a bad addiction. I'll let you interpret what that means... I'm not proud of it, but it was caused by problems in my personal life that I've now learned a lot from.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jeff Sekinger @jeffsekinger Fast forward a few years and was on and off with my addiction. had a corporate job at the biggest bank in America. And finally quit when my cubicle as was sitting in realized... "This isn't the life want to live."'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jeff Sekinger @jeffsekinger Corporate was hammering me for posting free finance content. The job also held me me back from what truly wanted out of life, which was freedom and to truly help others, Not just to stack some billionaire's pockets. That's when quit my job and started my first business.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jeff Sekinger @jeffsekinger It was a business centered around helping others with credit and funding. Our first month, we did $5k, then $10k, $25k, $50k, and it started blowing up. Now that business is doing millions in sales annually, and those| helped needed a place to invest the extra money they made.'.

Photo by Business Instantly on August 14, 2021. May be an image of text that says 'Jeff Sekinger @jeffsekinger Our clients always got great results on the credit side to get funding for businesses, investments etc. They saw that I've invested my own money into crypto as early as 2012, so they wanted to get in on the opportunity. Since our launch, we've got $40M in the fund and growing.'.
